window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A lot of strange things have happened to Azaria since she'd awoken to find herself a dungeon core. Going back in time will hopefully top the cake. With a better understanding of what awaits the Earth, Azaria decides to take things into her own hands to prevent the cruel fate. She just has to recruit some allies that want the same thing. It is a good thing the gods have made plenty of messes that they haven't cleaned up all over the universe. Using the artifact from the demon world, Azaria takes begins a quest of finding a needle in the haystack. Looking for anything that can help in her mission.</p>"; 
